<li id="cite_note-Romig_1994-22"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Romig_1994_22-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Romig_1994_22-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFRomig1994" class="citation journal cs1">Romig, Ronald (1994). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/43200958">"The Lamanite Mission"</a>. <i>The John Whitmer Historical Association Journal</i>. <b>14</b>: 29â31. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/43200958">43200958</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+John+Whitmer+Historical+Association+Journal&amp;rft.atitle=The+Lamanite+Mission&amp;rft.volume=14&amp;rft.pages=29-31&amp;rft.date=1994&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F43200958%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft.aulast=Romig&amp;rft.aufirst=Ronald&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F43200958&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOrigin+of+Latter+Day+Saint+polygamy" class="Z3988"></span></span>
