<li id="cite_note-68"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-68">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">When <a href="/wiki/Heber_C._Kimball" title="Heber C. Kimball">Heber C. Kimball</a> asked Snow the question if she was not a virgin although married to Joseph Smith, she replied, "I thought you knew Joseph Smith better than that.": <a href="/wiki/Angus_M._Cannon" title="Angus M. Cannon">Angus M. Cannon</a>, statement of interview with Joseph Smith III, 23, LDS Church Archives.</span>
