<li id="cite_note-JOAH-107"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-JOAH_107-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">The <a href="/wiki/Journal_of_American_History" class="mw-redirect" title="Journal of American History">Journal of American History</a>'s review of Clark's book states that "<i>1844</i> is fairly accurate and perceptive." <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFFrank_Otto_GatellPessen1970" class="citation cs2">Frank Otto Gatell; <a href="/wiki/Edward_Pessen" title="Edward Pessen">Pessen, Edward</a> (1970), "Review [untitled]", <i><a href="/wiki/Journal_of_American_History" class="mw-redirect" title="Journal of American History">Journal of American History</a></i>, <b>57</b> (2), Organization of American Historians: 426â428, <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F1918185">10.2307/1918185</a>, <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/1918185">1918185</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+American+History&amp;rft.atitle=Review+%5Buntitled%5D&amp;rft.volume=57&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=426-428&amp;rft.date=1970&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F1918185&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F1918185%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft.au=Frank+Otto+Gatell&amp;rft.au=Pessen%2C+Edward&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOrigin+of+Latter+Day+Saint+polygamy" class="Z3988"></span></span>
